sequenceDiagram
    participant API as DefaultMQProducer
    participant P as DefaultMQProducerImpl
    participant F as MQFaultStrategy
    participant C as MQClientAPIImpl
    participant N as NettyRemotingClient
    participant S as SendMessageProcessor
    participant M as DefaultMessageStore

    API->>P: send(message)
    P->>P: sendDefaultImpl()
    P->>P: tryToFindTopicPublishInfo()
    P->>F: selectOneMessageQueue()
    P->>P: sendKernelImpl()
    P->>C: sendMessage()
    C->>N: invokeSync / invokeAsync / invokeOneway
    N->>S: SEND_MESSAGE
    S->>M: asyncPutMessage()
    M-->>P: PutMessageResult → SendResult
